Installing DeepSeek AI Assistant on Huawei Mobile Devices

DeepSeek is available on Huawei AppGallery, as confirmed by an official Huawei forum post. That means you can download it directly through AppGallery on your Huawei phone or tablet  .

To install:

1. Open AppGallery on your Huawei device.


2. Search for DeepSeek.


3. Tap Install, grant the necessary permissions, and complete setup.




‚ö†Ô∏è Privacy Concern:

Several users on Reddit raised privacy issues‚Äîreporting that "DeepSeek‚Äôs popular AI app is explicitly sending user data back to servers in China"  . If your privacy is a concern, please keep that in mind.



